name: Trade Show Heatmapping
tagline: Heatmapping of Attendees inside a Trade Show
body:
### Welcome!
This page contains the source code for displaying heatmap of users locations in a Tradeshow.

### Technologies used
* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* jQuery 1.7
* D3.js


### Authors and Contributors
This project is managed and contributed by @Parithi.
